    <title>New contest proposal</title>
    <link>https://forum.moparisthebest.com/t/new-contest-proposal/431610</link>
    <description>How about an EGA-contest? It would differ greatly from the last one, instead of having a specific theme, the ruleset would be as follows:

64-colour EGA palette 
Max 16 different colours on each frame
40x30 canvas for rendering

It would be a fun challenge to do graphics on such a small scale, and have it done in a decent fashion. I&#39;ve thrown together a library for Java that does just this (programmatically generate the palette and a font engine).

Report any interest here.</description>
    
